Great excitement and the promise of rain with a chopper circling overhead and the odd dash of elegance characterised happenings at Jack Botes hall in the city where the State of the Province Address (Sopa) proceedings are underway.
From early guests filled the public gallery to witness Premier Stan Mathabatha deliver his customary speech marking the opening of the Legislature.
Update to follow.
